### ==========================================
### Northwind Order Management API — Test Requests
### Base URL: http://localhost:5281/api
### ==========================================

### --- Customers ---

### List all customers
GET http://localhost:5281/api/customers
Accept: application/json

### Search customers by name
GET http://localhost:5281/api/customers/search?q=Alfred
Accept: application/json

### --- Employees ---

### List all employees
GET http://localhost:5281/api/employees
Accept: application/json

### --- Shippers ---

### List all shippers
GET http://localhost:5281/api/shippers
Accept: application/json

### --- Products ---

### Search products
GET http://localhost:5281/api/products/search?q=chai
Accept: application/json

### --- Orders ---

### List orders (paginated)
GET http://localhost:5281/api/orders?page=1&pageSize=10
Accept: application/json

### List orders with filters
GET http://localhost:5281/api/orders?page=1&pageSize=10&customerId=ALFKI&region=Western Europe
Accept: application/json

### Get order by ID
GET http://localhost:5281/api/orders/10248
Accept: application/json

### Create a new order
POST http://localhost:5281/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerId": "ALFKI",
  "employeeId": 1,
  "orderDate": "2026-04-27",
  "shipName": "Alfreds Futterkiste",
  "shipStreet": "Obere Str. 57",
  "shipCity": "Berlin",
  "shipRegion": null,
  "shipPostalCode": "12209",
  "shipCountry": "Germany",
  "freight": 32.38,
  "lines": [
    { "productId": 11, "quantity": 12, "discount": 0 },
    { "productId": 42, "quantity": 10, "discount": 0.05 }
  ]
}

### Update an order (replace ORDER_ID with actual ID)
PUT http://localhost:5281/api/orders/11078
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "orderId": 11078,
  "customerId": "ALFKI",
  "employeeId": 2,
  "shipperId": 1,
  "shipName": "Alfreds Futterkiste - Updated",
  "shipStreet": "Obere Str. 57",
  "shipCity": "Berlin",
  "shipRegion": null,
  "shipPostalCode": "12209",
  "shipCountry": "Germany",
  "freight": 45.00,
  "lines": [
    { "productId": 11, "quantity": 20, "discount": 0.1 }
  ]
}

### Delete an order (replace ORDER_ID with actual ID)
DELETE http://localhost:5281/api/orders/11078

### --- Geocoding ---

### Validate an address
GET http://localhost:5281/api/geocoding/validate?street=1600+Amphitheatre+Parkway&city=Mountain+View&country=USA
Accept: application/json

### --- Invoices ---

### Download invoice PDF
GET http://localhost:5281/api/invoices/10248
Accept: application/pdf

### --- Analytics ---

### Orders over time (all years)
GET http://localhost:5281/api/analytics/orders-over-time
Accept: application/json

### Orders over time (filtered by year)
GET http://localhost:5281/api/analytics/orders-over-time?year=1997
Accept: application/json

### Shipments by region (top 10 countries)
GET http://localhost:5281/api/analytics/shipments-by-region
Accept: application/json

### Available years for filtering
GET http://localhost:5281/api/analytics/available-years
Accept: application/json